Class ApfloatHolder

java.lang.Object
org.apfloat.samples.ApfloatHolder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ApfloatHolder extends Object implements Serializable
Simple JavaBean to hold one Apfloat. This class can also be thought of as a pointer to an Apfloat.
Version:
1.9.0
Author:
